reviewText: I chose this rating, because I absolutely LOVE Madame and her stories:-) I was so glad I was able to find and purchase this movie:-) I only wish Madame and Wayland Flowers could have made more ABSOLUTELY HILARIOUS movies together:'( I love this movie

This will make you laugh. I nearly scream laughing at some things they say.  Madame has a lot to say and boy does she say it. Not for the kids. I particularly laugh about her joke regarding dicker and dicker of Beverly Hills.
